                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 40.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 9th May</hi>, 1842, <hi rend="italic">confined three months</hi>)—he is the man—he has been summarily convicted since.</p>
